Definition: sharing the risk by insurance companies
Example: part or all of the insurer's risk is assumed by other companies in return for part of the premium paid by the insured; reinsurance enables a client to get coverage that would be too great for any one company to assume
Synonyms: verb, communication, reinsure, insurance, sharing, the, risk, by, companies, part, or, all, of, insurer, s, is, assumed, other, in, return, for, premium, paid, insured, enables, a, client, to, get, coverage, that, would, be, too, great, any, one, company, assume
Category: noun.possession
